<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <%- include('../layout/_head.ejs')%>
</head>

<body>

    <div id="wrap">

        <%- include('../layout/_header.ejs')%>

        <div id="container-block">
            <main id="content" role="main" data-dep1="issues" data-dep2="card" data-dep3="">

                <div class="sub-visual">
                    <div class="container">
                        <h2 class="page-title">Card News</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <%- include('../layout/_location.ejs')%>
                <div class="container">
                    <form action="">
                        <fieldset>
                            <legend>SEARCH</legend>
                            <div class="board-search">
                                <div class="row row-10">
                                    <div class="col-auto">
                                        <select name="s" id="lbl2" class="custom-select custom-select-lg">
                                            <option value="searchAll" selected="">제목+내용</option>
                                            <option value="searchTitle">제목</option>
                                            <option value="searchContent">내용</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="KEYWORDS">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-auto">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-gray">SEARCH</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </fieldset>
                    </form>
                    <div class="count">
                        <span>Total</span>
                        <i>8</i>
                        <span>Page</span>
                        <i>2</i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-news">
                        <div class="row">
                            <% for(var i = 0; i < 5; i++){ %>
                            <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-3">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <a href="cardDetail.html" class="img">
                                        <img src="https://www.kwdi.re.kr/upload/editor/CM030/CM03020211005075244WAJEL.jpg" alt="">
                                    </a>
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <a href="" class="card-title">[한국여성정책연구원 카드뉴스] 남녀 청소년과 디지털문화</a>
                                        <p class="card-text"><span class="text-muted">2021-09-30</span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-3">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <a href="cardDetail.html" class="img">
                                        <img src="https://www.kwdi.re.kr/upload/editor/CM030/CM03020210913104627AQSOM.jpg" alt="">
                                    </a>
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <a href="" class="card-title">
                                            [한국여성정책연구원 카드뉴스] 코로나19 시기, 돌봄과 퇴직 이중고를 경험하고 있는 엄마들</a>
                                        <p class="card-text"><span class="text-muted">2021-07-31</span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <%- include('../layout/_pagination.ejs')%>
                </div>

            </main>
        </div>

        <%- include('../layout/_footer.ejs')%>

    </div>


    <script>
    </script>

</body>

</html>